useful :
xwallpaper (set wallpaper using xorg)
disown (used with &, allows to kill a job)
awk
sed
scrot (screenshot)
sxhkd (hotkey deamon)
feh / sxiv (image viewer)
xprop (info window)
ripgrep (grep but way faster)
lsblk (show every devices plugged in)
xrandr
xev (gives info about a key)
screenkey (shows key pressed)

date
cal (calendar)

df -h (hard disk info)
du -h (size file or dir)
uname (info about the system)
pidof *program* (returns pid of the prog)
gotop

exa (ls but faster)

